<para style="q1">

<verse number="3" style="v" />You return man to dust,</para>

<para style="q1">and you say, "Return, you descendants of mankind."</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="4" style="v" />For a thousand years in your sight</para>

<para style="q1">are as yesterday when it is past,</para>

<para style="q1">and as a watch in the night.</para>
